snippet.title: Urban Trial Playground Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Urban Trial Playground is taking the action from city streets, straight to the sunny and colorful beaches of California, mixing in even more crazy tricks, flips and combos than ever before. It’s a game of speed, balance and style! Launching exclusively on Nintendo Switch on April 5.

#Nintendo #NintendoSwitch #UrbanTrialPlayground
